{"tid":2429122,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Jennie被爆戀GD後首更新IG 撐隊友Rosé新碟","createTime":"2021-03-02T05:43:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T08:26:03.000Z","uid":16659,"like":14,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"985d89729bd1f160b20e338fde55ee29e9ccd4da","tid":2429122,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T05:43:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/14QuugoYWWdHylGva5QDMvqtxl4=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WZCQOQDWCRFGXKSHBE3FBB2OIE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F14QuugoYWWdHylGva5QDMvqtxl4%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWZCQOQDWCRFGXKSHBE3FBB2OIE.jpg&h=0255e04a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓國女團BLACK PINK的25歲成員Jennie，上月被爆暗撻同門師兄、天團BIGBANG的32歲隊長G-DRAGON（GD）一年，兩人所屬的YG事務所亦沒有直接否認戀情。<br />\n<br />\n冇回應戀情<br />\n爆出戀情後Jennie及GD一直未有更新IG，至昨晚Jennie終於首度更新IG，於IG的限時動態公開隊友Ros&eacute;首張個人專輯的宣傳海報，力撐隊友12日推出的新碟，不過Jennie就未有公開自己的新相，亦沒有正面回應戀情。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/t9SnhfOzAt9JdwVWP-CLORUOciw=/802x1059/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XRGAPEKJKZBXBOJ4K3GJRQWPLM.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ft9SnhfOzAt9JdwVWP-CLORUOciw%3D%2F802x1059%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXRGAPEKJKZBXBOJ4K3GJRQWPLM.JPG&h=3de8b938&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/mKG1_pHC6szvDCkF8uuQnzYuaZU=/802x1408/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/I2MHUISK2VE4JEMQMOILHIXEB4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FmKG1_pHC6szvDCkF8uuQnzYuaZU%3D%2F802x1408%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfro